<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 22:06:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>民意调查显示，90％的犹太人认为在不久的将来会爆发与以色列阿拉伯人的家庭暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/90-of-jews-see-domestic-violence-erupting-with-israeli-arabs-in-near-future-poll-shows/0000018b-d43f-d168-a3ef-d5ffccf20000</link><description>协议中心进行的民意调查显示，犹太人和阿拉伯社区的相互不信任激增。 “10 月 7 日的集体创伤将影响未来几年各群体之间的关系”</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 21:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/90-of-jews-see-domestic-violence-erupting-with-israeli-arabs-in-near-future-poll-shows/0000018b-d43f-d168-a3ef-d5ffccf20000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列和哈马斯在释放人质人数、战斗暂停持续时间方面存在分歧，谈判陷入僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-disagree-on-number-of-released-hostages-duration-of-fighting-pause/0000018b-d478-d168-a3ef-d5fa08a90000</link><description>外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，哈马斯寻求释放约 50 名人质，其中主要是妇女和儿童，以换取释放巴勒斯坦女性和未成年囚犯。以色列要求大幅增加人质人数</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 21:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-disagree-on-number-of-released-hostages-duration-of-fighting-pause/0000018b-d478-d168-a3ef-d5fa08a90000</guid></item><item><title>“甘茨离开政府的那一刻，内塔尼亚胡的沙漏就翻转了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-minute-gantz-leaves-the-government-the-hourglass-is-turned-over/0000018b-d383-d423-affb-f3a34bf40000</link><description>要求甘茨开始计划退出紧急政府的不仅仅是政治利益。甘茨的退出策略也符合国家利益</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 20:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-minute-gantz-leaves-the-government-the-hourglass-is-turned-over/0000018b-d383-d423-affb-f3a34bf40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女奋力打破全球对哈马斯性暴力的沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-15/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-fight-to-break-global-silence-on-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018b-d418-d168-a3ef-d5fa55000000</link><description>与许多其他领域一样，当谈到 10 月 7 日揭露哈马斯基于性别的暴力时，以色列公民介入了政府留下的巨大空白</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 19:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-15/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-fight-to-break-global-silence-on-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018b-d418-d168-a3ef-d5fa55000000</guid></item><item><title>新研究表明，大卫和所罗门的圣经王国可能确实存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-15/ty-article/david-and-solomons-biblical-kingdom-may-have-existed-after-all-new-study-suggests/0000018b-cddd-d518-a39b-fffd773b0000</link><description>圣经考古学家说，基泽的纪念性建筑的年代可追溯至公元前 10 世纪初，这意味着它们可能是所罗门建造的。但同事们仍持怀疑态度</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 19:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-15/ty-article/david-and-solomons-biblical-kingdom-may-have-existed-after-all-new-study-suggests/0000018b-cddd-d518-a39b-fffd773b0000</guid></item><item><title>地堡破坏者、炮弹和激光制导导弹：美国向以色列提供的弹药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/shells-laser-guided-missiles-and-bunker-busters-the-munitions-the-u-s-supplied-israel/0000018b-d3b9-dffa-adef-f7b990750000</link><description>五角大楼内部文件详细介绍了“以色列高级领导人”提出的弹药要求 ■ 国会民主党人对拜登政府缺乏透明度越来越警惕</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 17:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/shells-laser-guided-missiles-and-bunker-busters-the-munitions-the-u-s-supplied-israel/0000018b-d3b9-dffa-adef-f7b990750000</guid></item><item><title>高等法院无视政府立场，裁定犹太配偶的寡妇可以移民以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/defying-govt-position-high-court-rules-widows-of-jewish-spouse-can-immigrate-to-israel/0000018b-d21d-dffa-adef-f61d9c730000</link><description>内政部一直要求寡妇提供犹太生活方式的证明，才有资格遵守回归法，但这一条件已被高等法院最近的裁决驳回</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 17:36:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/defying-govt-position-high-court-rules-widows-of-jewish-spouse-can-immigrate-to-israel/0000018b-d21d-dffa-adef-f61d9c730000</guid></item><item><title>加沙变成废墟：世界上最大的巴勒斯坦城市很快将无法居住</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-in-ruins-the-largest-palestinian-city-in-the-world-soon-uninhabitable/0000018b-d3a4-d423-affb-f3a70ff40000</link><description>无论是在古代还是近代历史中，中东和世界各地的城市都曾经被摧毁过。对于各国来说，这是一场地震事件。正如 10 月 7 日改变了一切一样，加沙城的毁灭也将改变一切</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 16:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-in-ruins-the-largest-palestinian-city-in-the-world-soon-uninhabitable/0000018b-d3a4-d423-affb-f3a70ff40000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔调解的加沙以色列人质释放谈判取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/progress-reported-in-qatari-mediated-talks-to-free-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-d354-d423-affb-f3f7111d0000</link><description>据路透社周三报道，卡塔尔调解员正在寻求谈判一项协议，其中包括释放约 50 名人质，以换取为期三天的停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 15:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/progress-reported-in-qatari-mediated-talks-to-free-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-d354-d423-affb-f3f7111d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列渴望生命，就必须改变对巴勒斯坦人的态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-aspires-to-life-not-death-it-must-change-its-approach-to-the-palestinians/0000018b-d290-d423-affb-f3b3aac60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 14:33:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-aspires-to-life-not-death-it-must-change-its-approach-to-the-palestinians/0000018b-d290-d423-affb-f3b3aac60000</guid></item><item><title>“隐蔽的反犹太主义已变得完全公开”：以色列海外学生面临仇恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-antisemitism-has-become-totally-overt-israeli-students-abroad-face-hatred/0000018b-c8a3-d485-ab9b-ecf344350000</link><description>自以色列-加沙战争爆发以来，外国医学院的以色列学生报告称，他们发现自己受到攻击</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 14:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-antisemitism-has-become-totally-overt-israeli-students-abroad-face-hatred/0000018b-c8a3-d485-ab9b-ecf344350000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯屠杀了巴勒斯坦独立国家的梦想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-has-massacred-the-palestinian-dream-of-an-independent-state/0000018b-d28c-dffa-adef-f68c96400000</link><description>早在哈马斯发动袭击之前，两国解决方案就已处于生命末期，但 10 月 7 日的袭击很可能是两国解决方案棺材上的最后一颗钉子。对于以色列和巴勒斯坦的民族愿望来说，这都是一场悲剧</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 13:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-has-massacred-the-palestinian-dream-of-an-independent-state/0000018b-d28c-dffa-adef-f68c96400000</guid></item><item><title>伦敦画廊因反犹太主义言论推迟艾未未展览</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/london-gallery-postpones-exhibition-by-ai-weiwei-over-antisemitic-comments/0000018b-d2fb-dffa-adef-f6fb50670000</link><description>这位著名的中国持不同政见者在社交媒体上谈论犹太“媒体影响”和对以色列的数十亿美元援助资金，导致他原定在里森画廊举行的展览被推迟</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 13:01:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/london-gallery-postpones-exhibition-by-ai-weiwei-over-antisemitic-comments/0000018b-d2fb-dffa-adef-f6fb50670000</guid></item><item><title>加沙哈马斯政权的垮台不会损害伊朗的地区战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-fall-of-the-hamas-regime-in-gaza-wouldnt-harm-irans-regional-strategy/0000018b-d2b1-dffa-adef-f6b1e1860000</link><description>德黑兰与哈马斯和真主党等组织的关系并不是其安全概念的核心，因为它试图与中东各国政府建立联系</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 12:15:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/the-fall-of-the-hamas-regime-in-gaza-wouldnt-harm-irans-regional-strategy/0000018b-d2b1-dffa-adef-f6b1e1860000</guid></item><item><title>斯德哥尔摩电影节道歉并邀请美国-以色列电视创作者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/stockholm-film-festival-apologizes-extends-invite-to-u-s-israeli-tv-creator/0000018b-d24a-df9a-ab8b-deca7cec0000</link><description>有报道称，斯德哥尔摩国际电影节取消了女演员兼电视创作人阿莉扎·查诺维茨 (Aleeza Chanowitz) 的出席计划，该电影节的节目总监表示，“电影节绝不会因为政治原因而将电影从节目中删除”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 11:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/stockholm-film-festival-apologizes-extends-invite-to-u-s-israeli-tv-creator/0000018b-d24a-df9a-ab8b-deca7cec0000</guid></item><item><title>美国有史以来最大规模的亲以色列集会：华盛顿特区历史性集会的主要图片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/americas-biggest-pro-israel-rally-ever-images-from-historic-gathering-in-washington-d-c/0000018b-d2bb-dffa-adef-f6bbe4e80000</link><description>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件发生近六周后，数十万人涌向国家广场支持以色列，反犹太主义情绪高涨，加沙战争在国际社会的日益密切关注下持续进行</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 11:29:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/americas-biggest-pro-israel-rally-ever-images-from-historic-gathering-in-washington-d-c/0000018b-d2bb-dffa-adef-f6bbe4e80000</guid></item><item><title>BBC 就以色列针对加沙医院的医务人员和讲阿拉伯语的误报道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/bbc-apologizes-for-reporting-that-israel-targeted-medics-in-gaza-hospital/0000018b-d297-d168-a3ef-d7ff8e760000</link><description>英国广播公司(BBC)发表澄清称，该错误“低于我们的编辑标准”，并将错误归因于其错误引用了路透社的报道</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 11:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/bbc-apologizes-for-reporting-that-israel-targeted-medics-in-gaza-hospital/0000018b-d297-d168-a3ef-d7ff8e760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙是否遵守国际法？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-israel-abiding-by-international-law-in-gaza/0000018b-ce5e-d168-a3ef-dffe16ee0000</link><description>哈马斯使以色列国防军在医院和学校之外开展活动时难以遵守国际战争法。法律专家对迄今为止军队在加沙的行为进行了评价：“强烈怀疑这是一次蓄意的不成比例的袭击”</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 11:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-israel-abiding-by-international-law-in-gaza/0000018b-ce5e-d168-a3ef-dffe16ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列顶级讽刺电视节目嘲笑 BBC 对以色列与哈马斯战争的报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/israels-top-satirical-tv-show-mocks-bbc-coverage-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d286-df9a-ab8b-deceb7150000</link><description>“哈马斯自由战士和平攻击以色列 39 天后，我们现在对其领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔进行了独家采访，”Eretz Nehederet 的 BBC 主持人在三分半钟的短片中说道</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 10:56:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/israels-top-satirical-tv-show-mocks-bbc-coverage-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d286-df9a-ab8b-deceb7150000</guid></item><item><title>“逐层搜查”：目击者描述以色列对加沙希法医院的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/floor-by-floor-searches-eyewitnesses-describe-raid-on-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-d275-d168-a3ef-d7ffa7ed0000</link><description>一名目击者称，以色列军队“完全控制”了医院，但补充说，医院内听不到枪声</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Nov 2023 10:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-15/ty-article/.premium/floor-by-floor-searches-eyewitnesses-describe-raid-on-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-d275-d168-a3ef-d7ffa7ed0000</guid></item></channel></rss>